--TEARDOWN--
#
# NOTE: the six different sizes above is to cover for different sizes in the version string
#
#       19614|19615|19616|19617|19618|19619|19620:
#
#       19614:   d.d.d
#       19615:   d.dd.d
#       19620:   d.dd.d-next

brokerStop CB
accumulatorStop
dbDrop CB
